Problem statement
Given a number ‘N’ and a number ‘K’. Return true if ‘K’th bit of number is set, else return false.

Example:
Input: ‘N’ = 5, ‘K’ = 1

Output: YES

SOLUTION:-
bool isKthBitSet(int n, int k)
{
    // Write your code here.
    
    if ((n & (1 << k-1)) != 0) {
        return true;
    }
    else {
        return false;
    }
}
